" Finally an older gentleman ( surprise , surprise ) easily named the Senate and House of Representatives . Who is the current vice president ? " Uhhh ... Obama ? " " Joe Biden ? " What 's the longest river in America ? " I 'm not sure . " " I 'm not even sure . I 'm gon na go with a guess — Lake Michigan ! " What are the three branches of government ? Folks did a little better with this question . One woman almost got all three : " Judicial , executive ... I ca n't …
